About Me

Hello! I am Ishaaq Ziyan and I am a professional Blockchain Developer certified by Moralis, An avid Investor and Researcher in the crypto space. I have been studying Cryptography, Blockchain Engineering and Reverse Engineering in different algorithms since 2018, and after much research and dedication, I started investing in the space in 2019. I am currently Studying for the Higher Educational Qualification which is conducted by the BCS | The Chartered Institute for IT. Also, I invest in blockchain startups which I think might have a very good potential and a set of use cases.
